<main class="site-main site-main--locked" aria-labelledby="home-title">
  <p class="eyebrow">Jared Harbison</p>
  <h1 id="home-title">Software Engineer</h1>

  <p class="lede">
    Senior Software Engineer building and owning product-focused web applications
    from concept through production.
  </p>

  <p>
    I work across product planning, architecture, implementation, and delivery,
